org.bytedeco.hdf5

Class IdComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.hdf5.IdComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataSpace, H5Location, PropList

    @Namespace(value="H5")
 @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=hdf5.class)
public class IdComponent
extends Pointer
    \class IdComponent \brief Class IdComponent provides wrappers of the C functions that operate on an HDF5 identifier.

    In most cases, the C library handles these operations and an application rarely needs them.
